  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0baf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fertilizer Distribution Today by India - Ministry of Agriculture",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Agriculture has informed that the amount of urea fertilizer received by the Government of India to Sri Lanka will be distributed from today.",
        "Landing of fertilizer from the fertilizer ship which arrived in the country a few days ago from India has been completed.",
        "In this case, the Anath Ministry has further informed that they expect to distribute and complete them within the next 10 days.",
        "Regarding the quality of the said fertilizer, a special test was conducted yesterday and a certificate has been issued that the amount of fertilizer is of appropriate quality.",
        "Director General of National Fertilizer Secretariat Chandana Lokhu Hevake said that a 50 kg fertilizer bag will be available to the farmers for 10,000 rupees."
      ],
